                Aurelia Aureliana <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iva</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ecit</ex></expan> Aurelio Iantullo <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>fra</abbr><ex>tri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>car</abbr><ex>issimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>ob</abbr><ex>ito</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XXX
